      <title>中国消费者价格自八月以来首次上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-09/china-s-consumer-prices-rise-for-first-time-since-august</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的消费者价格自八月以来首次上涨，打破了使世界第二大经济体的增长潜力面临压力的连续收缩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-09/china-s-consumer-prices-rise-for-first-time-since-august</guid>
