      <title>花旗集团正在寻找私人信贷公司提供 Peloton 贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-09/citigroup-c-in-talks-with-private-credit-firms-for-peloton-pton-loan</link>
